{"tid":465849,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林卓廷促英國就港普選表態","createTime":"2017-11-12T03:59:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-12T05:32:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3084cb83f38b12ec73e24eaedf874601637e68c5","tid":465849,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T03:59:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171112/20211714\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171112%2F20211714&d=uOfuyJdyU270d4KIX3wekNWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=9954d67c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171112%2F20211714&h=95766e1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171112/20211714</a><br />\n<br />\n林卓廷促英國就港普選表態<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171112/large/a0304a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171112%2Flarge%2Fa0304a.gif&h=d6fab74b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林卓廷（左）昨與英國外交官Warren Leigh會面，談及港社運人士和年輕領袖被檢控。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】正在英國的民主黨立法會議員林卓廷，繼日前到英國National Crime Agency舉報前特首梁振英涉貪，昨又到英國外交部與負責香港事務官員見面，要求英國政府就北京違背承諾，未有在港實施普選表達明確清晰態度，並要求英國稅務及海關局，徹查梁振英UGL案，而英方關注有立會議員被取消議席、以及年輕社運人士被檢控事件。<br />\n<br />\n與外交部代表會晤<br />\n<br />\n林卓廷昨與英國外交部負責香港事務代表Warren Leigh會面，雙方會面約一小時。林在會面後稱，他向Warren Leigh表達對香港情況強烈憂慮，要求英國密切關注中英聯合聲明及一國兩制的實踐的情況，並就中國政府違背承諾沒有讓香港實施普選，要求英國政府明確及清晰表態，敦促英方不要要求港人接受假普選方案。<br />\n<br />\n另外，林又要求Warren Leigh向英國稅務及海關局轉達徹查梁振英UGL案訴求，對方答允將資料轉交英國稅務及海關局主席跟進。林形容Warren Leigh關注及熟悉本港政治情況，尤其關注本港立法會議員被取消議席及一眾社運人士和年輕領袖被檢控的事情，雙方都作很深入的交流。<br />\n<br />\n■記者莫劍弦"},{"pid":"4af3fda72440c0278c36383df52e10390fad493d","tid":465849,"uid":59773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T05:32:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}